WEBVTT

00:03:28.247 --> 00:03:30.388
But really, what do you do, right?

00:03:30.388 --> 00:03:32.413
Some write blogs, some ignore it,

00:03:32.413 --> 00:03:34.145
some join protests.

00:03:34.145 --> 00:03:36.710
I did all of it. In fact, that was what everyone was doing

00:03:36.710 --> 00:03:38.388
two years ago.

00:03:38.388 --> 00:03:41.367
So the media was filled with stories about

00:03:41.367 --> 00:03:43.133
all the horrific deeds

00:03:43.133 --> 00:03:45.237
that Indian men are capable of.

00:03:45.237 --> 00:03:46.472
They were compared to animals,

00:03:46.472 --> 00:03:48.659
sexually repressed beasts.

00:03:48.659 --> 00:03:52.663
In fact, so alien and unthinkable was this event

00:03:52.663 --> 00:03:53.977
in an Indian mind

00:03:53.977 --> 00:03:56.393
that the response from the Indian media,

00:03:56.393 --> 00:04:00.300
public and politicians proved one point: